---
---

<section class="section" id="accommodation">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="accommodation-hero text-center">
      <h2>Handbuilt Spaces Designed for Sleeping Well and Loving Life</h2>
      <p>
        Maceda was built by João in the mid-2000s using reclaimed materials, shaped by the forest and ocean around it.
        It wasn't designed as a business, but as a low-impact space to live simply and close to nature.
        When friends stayed longer and left more grounded than when they arrived, it grew naturally from there.
      </p>
      <p>
        It's simple, creative and comfortable.
        A place where you'll sleep well, slow down and start planning your return before you leave.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img src="/images/rooms.png" alt="Maceda Surf Camp rooms" class="rooms-image" loading="lazy" />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split split--reverse">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/fotos.png" alt="Maceda Surf Camp interior" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Nothing Fancy… Just Really, Really Comfy</h2>
        <ul class="comfort-list">
          <li>Flexible accommodation for solo travellers, couples, and groups</li>
          <li>Comfortable, calm spaces with good beds and clean rooms (no hostel chaos)</li>
          <li>Thoughtfully designed communal areas for relaxing, connecting or doing nothing at all</li>
          <li>A quiet and peaceful outdoor area surrounded by greenery</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#book" class="btn" >Book Now!</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/garden.png" alt="Maceda Surf Camp garden" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Like Your Grandma's Garden... Only Cooler</h2>
        <ul class="amenities">
          <li>Fibre-optic Wi-Fi throughout the camp</li>
          <li>Free private parking</li>
          <li>Healthy breakfast (vegetarian, vegan and gluten-free friendly)</li>
          <li>Fully equipped kitchen</li>
          <li>Train station nearby with easy access to Porto</li>
          <li>Supermarket 5 minutes away</li>
          <li>Outdoor yoga shala</li>
          <li>Forest trails</li>
          <li>Bonfire area</li>
          <li>Ping-pong, hammocks, volleyball and lounge spaces</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#book" class="btn" >Book Now!</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .accommodation-hero {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  .accommodation-hero p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .rooms-image {
    border-radius: 12px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .comfort-list, .amenities {
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .comfort-list li, .amenities li {
    padding: 0.35rem 0 0.35rem 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .comfort-list li::before, .amenities li::before {
    content: '•';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
</style>
